  augment "/emael:ManagedElement/GNBDUFunction/UeCC/UeBb/UeBbProfile" {
    list UeBbProfileUeCfg {
      description "Additional definitions from MOM:min/max-elements:0/16; Configuration of UE Baseband profile for UE groups. Instance UeBbProfileUeCfg=Base is created automatically when parent MO instance is created, unless created manually in same transaction. Attributes prefUeGroupList, ueGroupList and ueConfGroupList must be empty in instance UeBbProfileUeCfg=Base but cannot all be empty in any other instance of UeBbProfileUeCfg under same parent UeBbProfile instance. A combination of an element of ueGroupList and an element of prefUeGroupList in UeBbProfileUeCfg instance must be unique under UeBbProfile instance. Value 0 is no longer allowed and is planned to be removed from the valid range of prefUeGroupList and ueGroupList. Precondition: Instance UeBbProfileUeCfg=Base can only be created in same transaction as parent MO instance and cannot be deleted unless parent MO instance is deleted. Other instances can be created and deleted at any time. Maximum 15 UeBbProfileUeCfg instances, with RDN different from Base, can be created under parent MO instance. To be able to create an instance, the total number of instances, including all auto created instances, must be less than the total allowed number of instances under a GNBDUFunction instance that is 64.";
      key "ueBbProfileUeCfgId";
      leaf ueBbProfileUeCfgId {
        type leafref {
